"list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(192, 0, 0);">在一些征婚网站，不少离过婚的单.身.女.人列出的再婚条件之一是：男.方.性-能-力强。</span> </p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; list-style: none; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; line-height: 22px;"><br style="max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; list-style: none; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; line-height: 22px;">凡事有因必有果，有果必有因。<strong style="max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-weight: normal; list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(192, 0, 0);">尽管已婚女-人红.杏.出.墙给丈夫戴绿帽的原因是多种的，但其中最根本的原因是：丈夫没有给她满足满意的性爱。其实，多数女人出轨都是为了寻找理想的性爱。</span></strong>所谓“女人出-轨是为情”，只不过是女人们为.了.性.而自找的理由或借口，也是披着一块叫作“爱情”的遮羞布而已。所以，被戴了绿帽的男人们，应当从自己身上找原因，该好好想想，怎样才让自己的女-人不被别的男.人趁虚而入？</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; list-style: none; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; line-height: 22px;"><br style="max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; list-style: none; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; line-height: 22px;"><img src="http://www.wyt66.com/kindeditor/attached/image/20151025/20151025122510_321.jpg" alt="" style="border-style: none; border-width: initial; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important;"/> 